            <title><![CDATA[【图集】中国新型长征八号火箭亮相]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay"> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/926c-kffctcc6294709.jpg?itok=_24-Q-W6" alt data-caption="一路相送长征八号火箭的试验队队员。（中国航天科技集团）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/926c-kffctcc6294709.jpg?itok=_24-Q-W6" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>一路相送长征八号火箭的试验队队员。（中国航天科技集团）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/7356-kffctcc6294422.jpg?itok=BS-cS2Cm" alt data-caption="新型长征八号运载火箭。（中国航天科技集团）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/7356-kffctcc6294422.jpg?itok=BS-cS2Cm" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>新型长征八号运载火箭。（中国航天科技集团）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/6f6c-kffctcc6294512.jpg?itok=YpnelXxt" alt data-caption="新型长征八号运载火箭。（中国航天科技集团）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202012/20201216/6f6c-kffctcc6294512.jpg?itok=YpnelXxt" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>新型长征八号运载火箭。（中国航天科技集团）</p></figcaption></div><div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div></div>

<p>由中国航天科技集团有限公司一院研制的新型长征八号运载火箭在中国文昌航天发射场完成技术区相关工作后，垂直转运至发射区，计划于12月底择机实施飞行试验任务。</p>

<p>据新浪军事报道，今天上午8时20分，承载着长征八号运载火箭的活动发射平台，驶出发射场垂直测试厂房，平稳行驶，安全转运至发射区。后续，火箭将加注推进剂，按计划实施发射。</p>

<div class="center">
<figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="2bd1-kffctcc6294041_Large.jpg" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201130/2bd1-kffctcc6294041_Large.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>新型长征八号运载火箭。（中国航天科技集团）</figcaption></figure>
</div>

<p>长征八号运载火箭为两级半构型，火箭捆绑两个助推器。长征八号可以进一步完善新一代运载火箭型谱，满足未来中低轨高密度发射任务需求。</p>
